Name: VNC Viewer
Author: RealVNC <noreply@realvnc.com>
More:
VNC Viewer, from RealVNC, the original inventor of VNC technology, is remote access
 software that enables you to securely connect to and control a remote
 computer.
 RealVNC recommends the realvnc-vnc-server package (VNC Server) for the
 remote computer, for seamless, secure and reliable connections. A free trial
 is available.
